{"tid":1991814,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【正股驚閪】千金散盡買滙豐　股價插痛老翁心","createTime":"2020-04-27T16:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T01:14:54.000Z","uid":232237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cee2b2274c930606f0e8a91b0e30784f15abac3f","tid":1991814,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"千金散盡買滙豐 一殼眼淚<br />\n<br />\n絶望 唔溝貨<br />\n<br />\n300元 1拆3 無沽<br />\n<br />\n07年 153.5元 無沽<br />\n<br />\n沽樓 再買滙豐<br />\n<br />\n結果&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他續說：「我買滙豐買了超過20年，90年代開始買，成本價已無法計，我好長情，未分拆前300元買過，她拆細過，上過153元，我都一路增持，今天真的<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不敢再溝貨</span></strong></strong>了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今次跌得好急，兩個星期跌20%，2008年時都驚，但彈得好快，今次估計一時三刻彈不回去，都有一輪時間，短期內上返50蚊都偷笑！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2629312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2629312&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Tv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=acd86eaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2629312</a>"},{"pid":"1461484712114df8d12e9bed641d9cffaebc09f8","tid":1991814,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"通常散戶唔敢溝貨時就係底<br />\n有底唔撈，$153時卻高追，傻的嗎？"},{"pid":"e4b43f0976b9edda3d35a7645aa97265e94e0e5c","tid":1991814,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"買得hsbc都係想收息啫 咁睇股價唔入銀河金沙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9eab3d072744103a01b729b334a2f049331c0f","tid":1991814,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"唔知校長宜家仲夠唔夠錢退休呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GrWu_8FG3z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGrWu_8FG3z8&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Tv6